'''RockMelt'''是一款[[網頁瀏覽器|網頁瀏覽器]]，以[[Chromium_(浏览器)|Chromium]]原始碼為基礎，由提姆·豪斯（Tim Howes，[[LDAP|LDAP]]的發明者之一）及艾瑞克·維夏（Eric Vishria）成立的同名公司所開發，並獲得曾開發[[Netscape|Netscape]]瀏覽器，目前為[[Facebook|Facebook]][[董事|董事]]的[[馬克·安德森|馬克·安德森]]（Marc Andreessen）資金贊助<ref>{{cite news |url=http://tech.chinatimes.com/2007Cti/2007Cti-News/Inc/2007cti-news-Tech-inc/Tech-Content/0%2C4703%2C12050902%2B122009081500307%2C00.html |title=網景創辦人再出發 |publisher=工商時報 |date=2009-08-15 |accessdate=2009-08-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820181636/http://tech.chinatimes.com/2007Cti/2007Cti-News/Inc/2007cti-news-Tech-inc/Tech-Content/0%2C4703%2C12050902%2B122009081500307%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-08-20 }}</ref>。

RockMelt號稱將是首款整合[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Twitter|Twitter]]等[[社交網站|社交網站]]功能的社交瀏覽器<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/digital/storypage.jsp?f_MAIN_ID=322&f_SUB_ID=2920&f_ART_ID=208546 |title=Netscape創立者︰我會回來的！ |publisher=聯合新聞網 |date=2009-08-18 |accessdate=2009-08-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100110222256/http://mag.udn.com/mag/digital/storypage.jsp?f_MAIN_ID=322&f_SUB_ID=2920&f_ART_ID=208546 |archivedate=2010-01-10 }}</ref>。

