* 2012年10月11日，推出iPad版<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.wired.com/business/2012/10/rockmelt-thinks-youre-ready-for-a-mobile-browser/ | title=Rockmelt Thinks You’re Ready for a Modern Mobile Browser | date=2012-10-11 | work=Wired | first=Steven | last=Levy | accessdate=2015-09-06 | archive-date=2014-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220160514/http://www.wired.com/business/2012/10/rockmelt-thinks-youre-ready-for-a-mobile-browser/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
